snippet.title: Phantom Blade Zero - Official Gameplay Trailer | Summer Game Fest 2024
snippet.description: New trailer of Phantom Blade Zero, giving a sneak peek to the latest development of the game, featuring never-shown-before footage depicting high-speed combat and multiple weapons, among other game play elements. Announcement of a World Tour Demo.
